    priceStr: "$199",
    summary: "The UDR is an incredible value for advanced users. It's an all-in-one router, switch (with PoE), and UniFi controller. It's only WiFi 6, but the software features are unmatched at this price.",
    pros: ["Enterprise-grade UniFi OS software", "Two PoE ports for cameras or APs", "Incredible value for the features"],
    cons: ["Often out of stock", "Limited to gigabit speeds and WiFi 6"]
